Package com.hemebiotech.analytics

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISymptomAnalyzer
    Implemented by classes that will analyze a raw symptom list and return the result in the form of a list of strings
    The returned list must be sorted and organized without any duplicates
    ISymptomReader
    Implemented by classes that will read raw symptom data from a source
    The return value from the operation is a list of strings that may contain many duplications The implementation does not need to order the list
    ISymptomWriter
    Implemented by classes that will write analyzed symptom data into a target
    The data must be provided in the form of a sorted and organized list of strings without any duplicates
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalyticsCounter
    Main class of Analytics project
    ReadSymptomDataFromFile
    Implements ISymptomReader to read raw symptom data from a file
    SymptomCounter
    Implements ISymptomAnalyzer to count symptoms and return a list of strings with symptoms and their number of occurrences, sorted alphabetically by default or with a custom comparator
    Symptoms
    This class encapsulate all the logic to read raw symptom data from a source, analyze it, and write the result into a target
    WriteSymptomDataIntoFile
    Implements ISymptomWriter to write analyzed symptom data into a file
